Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory184.png'}
{2: 'Cathy 6337', 3: 'Everyone, this is, the proud feature of Venus Splash Park—Morning Star Beach!'}
{2: 'Cathy 6337', 3: 'Please have fun and relax for now! We will be following the tour schedule and enter the theme park in one hour.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Have fun and relax, huh...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Cathy, are there still hostile mechanoids lurking around? Like the ones that just attacked you?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Cathy 6337', 3: 'They are, few. Bad colleagues, recently, occasionally appear.'}
{2: 'Cathy 6337', 3: 'An open air theme park—quiet, lively, choice for relaxation!'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Hmm, few indeed... No more Corrupted signals other than the ones we just defeated.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'So those were just a few strays, huh?', 3: '16'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Unsure. Not enough info to decide if we should stay on high alert or not.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I looked up the records of other Golden Age theme parks, and they don't seem to use that many mechanoids. So that might have just been a coincidence...", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Probably because a theme park is meant to accommodate tourists, right?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: "You only need enough mechanoids to satisfy the needs of human tourists. So you don't need a lot of 'em.", 4: '1'}
{2: "You're here as well, Ayla?", 3: '25'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Of course! I happened to be in a base nearby, so I applied to President Hassen to come over!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: "We recovered some pretty interesting relics from the operation in Kowloong, so Allen's interest for Earth has been growing—", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: "Anyway, I'm just here to play and have fun!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Aaaand I\'m not the only "uninvited guest!"', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: 'I was assigned here by President Hassen after returning to my envoy work.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Is Babylonia okay...', 3: '35', 4: "Everyone's here...", 5: '36'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: '...? Babylonia is okay.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: 'Celica said, "Next vacation might be in who-knows-how-long, so I might as well get everyone in on this."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: "That's what she said.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Well, it's good that we have more people to play with, right?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "DON'T! FORGET! BOUT! ME!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Are y'all planning to leave me behind?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'I heard about your vacation from 【kuroname】, and I sped it through with the Prez. Karenina, now here in the name of "reconstruction inspection"!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Karenina stands with her hands planted on her hips, glaring all over. She seems to be searching for someone.'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "...Where's Lucia? Don't think you can hide from me by going on some vacation! We'll settle this once and for all this time!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Karen's frame... looks a bit different than usual.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'I hopped over straight from the work site. No time to switch outta this specialized frame.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I didn\'t come on vacation to avoid you. I received a mission telling us to "wind down."', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "I see... So it's a contest of who winds down the best, huh? Alright then!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Whatever it is, and whatever reason you give. You're not getting away this time!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Lucia is Lucia! Even if her memory data's gone all wonky, she's still the same Lucia I'm gonna beat!", 4: '1'}
{2: "I don't think Karenina is even listening...", 3: '57'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: "Speaking of, I've been to various ruins, but it's my first time at a water park.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: 'We gotta have fun and play in a water park, right? So... how do we do that?', 4: '1'}
{2: '...We eat and drink, maybe?', 3: '62', 4: '...We walk around, maybe?', 5: '70'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Eat and drink... Only you can do that, right, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Well, our sensory receptors can experience taste too.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'But it is not accompanied by the human feeling of satiety and pleasure.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "...Well, it's still worth exploring this place, I think.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: '...Yeah, this place does seem worthy of exploration.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Let's see what discoveries lie in store for us!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Might as well. It's not like we're on an urgent mission right now.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory206.png'}
{3: 'A little earlier, on the same beach where the Babylonia crowd is playing around...'}
{3: "Looking up at the dark sky, reaching one's hand straight out."}
{3: 'Knowing not what one yearns for, bearing wishes for some things to come true.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland & Gabriel', 3: 'Miss Luna.', 4: '1', 5: '2'}
{3: '...Must be overthinking it.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Miss Alpha is herding the target, and he is moving along the anticipated route.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "As for me... The hunting grounds are ready. He will have no qualms dying with the funeral we've prepared him.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'You all know what to do. Yes?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Obliterate Shome.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: 'His death shall deter his savior.', 4: '1'}
